school shark
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:lemon fish, flake, also called tope a shark of Australian and New Zealand waters, similar to the dogfish, but larger
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: possible NZ distinction in universal term; southern tope; <i>Galeorhinus australis</i>
